com.googlecode.sarasvati
Interface JoinResult

All Known Implementing Classes:
CompleteJoinResult
public interface JoinResult

Encapsulates the results of a join attempt. Includes whether or not the join is complete. If the join is complete, also includes the list of arc tokens which completed the join.

Author:
Paul Lorenz

Field Summary

getArcTokensCompletingJoin

List<ArcToken> getArcTokensCompletingJoin()
Returns the ArcTokens which were required to complete this join, and will be considered the parents of the new NodeToken. If isJoinComplete() would return false, this method should throw an IllegalStateException.

Returns:
The ArcTokens which were required to complete this join, and will be considered the parents of the new NodeToken.
Throws:
IllegalStateException - If this is invoked when isJoinComplete returns false.
